{"tid":2056561,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"［突然抗爭一週年］朋友作左首歌","createTime":"2020-06-08T19:01:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-09T03:50:19.000Z","uid":190239,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2633bf3a0e1ca0b03816f22a2cb7e942edc2a514","tid":2056561,"uid":190239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T19:01:53.000Z","msg":"出賣朋友系列<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果眼淚在眼前<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-d59OliCkuU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D-d59OliCkuU&d=N73AYdKZ8ITSJgwUZ5%2B19mo8q5%2FbnpuKyKF%2Fs7IAglk%3D&h=d382328b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-d59OliCkuU</a><br />\n<br />\n歌詞：<br />\n<br />\n這個荒誕的都市 為何沒有光線<br />\n城內每一天 黑暗在蔓延<br />\n彌漫著每一寸煙 滲透入照片<br />\n這一個夏季一切都改變<br />\n<br />\n理想的國度未浮現 和你那天的奮戰<br />\n就算未能兌現 仍有最美麗詩篇<br />\n<br />\n如果眼淚在眼前 要記得同伴總會在身邊<br />\n有些傷痛沒法倖免 但我慶幸有你並肩<br />\n就算沒法將壞事改變 也最少沒有對自己敷衍<br />\n<br />\n你我手裡的光線 從來沒有改變<br />\n傳遞到天邊 黑暗在面前<br />\n前路若已經擱淺 去建立人鏈<br />\n漆黑裡盛放 花已經開遍<br />\n<br />\n理想的國度未浮現 和你那天的奮戰<br />\n就算未能兌現 仍有最美麗詩篇<br />\n<br />\n如果眼淚在眼前 要記得同伴總會在身邊<br />\n有些傷痛沒法倖免 但我慶幸有你並肩<br />\n就算沒法將壞事改變 也最少沒有對自己敷衍<br />\n<br />\n假使世界已變遷<br />\n仍期望自由如飛燕<br />\n回來時便帶來新一天  <br />\n<br />\n如果眼淚在眼前 要記得同伴總會在身邊<br />\n有些傷痛沒法倖免 但我慶幸有你並肩<br />\n就算沒法將壞事改變 也最少沒有對自己敷衍<br />\n沒有對自己敷衍<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我想同所有一齊作戰嘅手足講<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">真係好慶幸有你地並肩作戰</span><br />\n<br />\n聽講唱個位絲打係靚女黎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好聽就屌我個friend算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">香港獨立 唯一出路</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"d2f26ed55b67a499a093222707179faec6a0fa78","tid":2056561,"uid":190239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T19:02:09.000Z","msg":"推1"},{"pid":"295aab11845de1783b051937257507eb604b0dcd","tid":2056561,"uid":190239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T19:02:21.000Z","msg":"推2"},{"pid":"ddb44c082e0adbecc16e82fd1a72502ce64ce710","tid":2056561,"uid":190239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T19:02:31.000Z","msg":"推3"},{"pid":"788ca1dc401ac54f1fa128bb85022ff7dc9bfe00","tid":2056561,"uid":190239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T19:03:54.000Z","msg":"推4"},{"pid":"b7e9d448977cc593feb58c480bec306d7c408e89","tid":2056561,"uid":360012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T19:07:53.000Z","msg":"就算沒法將壞事改變 也最少沒有對自己敷衍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6dcbff8431f751fe488122f32e6dc6fb79dcfe8","tid":2056561,"uid":190239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b7e9d448977cc593feb58c480bec306d7c408e89","tid":2056561,"uid":360012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T19:07:53.000Z","msg":"就算沒法將壞事改變 也最少沒有對自己敷衍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T01:22:52.000Z","msg":"呢句真係百感交集<br />\n有種無證騎士嘅感覺 <br />\n唔係贏唔贏到而係我要必須擋喺你面前"},{"pid":"b9a82cb44276b8e72e4bd1d276bde14a929ea01e","tid":2056561,"uid":245813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T01:26:23.000Z","msg":"啲收音會唔會差咗啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cacece16cad308194ee36159595399aed83adc64","tid":2056561,"uid":190239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b9a82cb44276b8e72e4bd1d276bde14a929ea01e","tid":2056561,"uid":245813,"like":0,